confOf#Trip: The trip is child of socialvent which is parented by workingevent and tutorial.
confOf#Banquet: The banquet is the child of socialvent which is the parent of reception.
confOf#Reception: The reception is a child of socialvent which is a child of an event.
confOf#Social_event: Socialvent is the parent of the banquet, the conference and reception. It is also the parent of the conference.
confOf#Event: The workingevent and the tutorial are both parented by the same event. The banquet and the administrative event are also parented by the same event.
confOf#Contribution: The contribution of a poster is the parent of a short paper and the child of a Thing.
confOf#Organization: The parent organization of the university is the company.
confOf#Person: The child of a Thing is the parent of an assistant and a member of the pc. The child is also the parent of a scholar and a regular person.
confOf#Company: The company is child of the organization which is parented by the university.
confOf#University: The university is the child of the organization which is parented by the company.
confOf#Scholar: The child of a scientist is the child of a scholar.
confOf#Administrator: The administrator is the child of the person who is the parent of the assistant.
confOf#Poster: The poster is a child of a Thing.
confOf#Paper: The paper is the child of the contribution which is the parent of the short paper.
confOf#Short_paper: The short paper is a child of contribution which is a child of Thing.
confOf#Reviewing_results_event: reviewingresultsevent is a child of administrativeevent which is parented by workingevent and conference.
confOf#Administrative_event: The administrativeevent is the parent of the banquet, the submissionevent and the registration of participants. It is also the parent of the socialevent and the reviewresultsevent.
confOf#Reviewing_event: reviewingevent is a child of administrativeevent and is parented by reviewingresultsevent.
confOf#Registration_of_participants_even: The registrationofparticipantsevent is a child of the administrativeevent which is parented by the reviewingevent.
confOf#Submission_event: The submissionevent is a child of the administrativeevent which is parented by the workingevent which is parented by the conference.
confOf#Camera_Ready_event: The camerareadyevent is a child of the administrativeevent which is the parent of the reviewingresultsevent.
confOf#Workshop: The child of a workingevent is a child of a social event which is also the parent of a trip.
confOf#Conference: Workingevent is the parent of a conference and a tutorial.
confOf#Tutorial: The workingevent is a child of the workingevent and is parented by the administrative event.
confOf#Working_event: The workingevent is the parent of the conference, the workshop and the tutorial. It is also the parent of the social event which is also the parent of the banquet.
confOf#Member: The child of the participant is the child of the person who is the parent of the administrator.
confOf#Participant: The child of the participant is the child of the chairpc, the student is the parent of the regular participant and the parent of the member.
confOf#Member_PC: memberpc is a child of the person who is the parent of the administrator.
confOf#Chair_PC: The chairpc is the child of the person who is the parent of a volunteer.
confOf#Student: The student is a child of a person who is also a child of a Thing.
confOf#Science_Worker: The child of a science worker is the parent of a scholar.
confOf#Assistant: The assistant is a child of a person who is also a child of a Thing.
confOf#Volunteer: The child of a volunteer is a child of a Thing.
confOf#Regular: The regular is the child of the participant who is the parent of the member.
confOf#Author: The author is a child of a person who is also a child of a Thing.
